title: All Attribute Martial Arts
description: All Attribute Martial Arts Manhua In his previous life, Wang Teng had offended dignitaries and caused his own family to be ruined. Even if he had no desire to resist, he was driven to extinction. After his death, Wang Teng was reborn into the world of martial arts with resentment and gained a golden finger that could pick up attributes. In my last life, I was a loser all my life, in this life, I will change my fate against the heavens!
